---
title: One-Pot Pho-Style Beef Meatball Soup with Veggie Noodles & Spiced Broth
description: To paraphrase Anthony Bourdain, a good bowl of pho will always make us happy. This iconic Vietnamese noodle soup has a heady broth, deep with beef flavor and fragrant with aromatics, that comes from simmering all day. It’s what inspired our riff with silky ribbons of zucchini and carrots in place of traditional rice noodles. Our shortcut version comes together in minutes instead of hours. Big, tender meatballs cook right in the pot, adding more beefy goodness to the broth—scented with ginger and lemongrass. Finish with a bright squeeze of lime juice and some chili flakes for a big bowl that’s as delicious as it is life affirming.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pot-pho-style-beef-meatball-soup-298a8019.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pot-pho-style-beef-meatball-soup-61cb246204b953527f52bd5c-d616d67f.pdf
